00:29:02.055 --> 00:29:03.818
that have been used on this
island.

00:29:03.818 --> 00:29:20.084
Like depleted uranium was
denied and then they admitted

00:29:20.084 --> 00:29:21.588
it.
 

00:29:21.588 --> 00:29:22.973
Video voiceover:
In my experience in dealing

00:29:22.973 --> 00:29:24.220
with hazardous sites and toxic
substances,

00:29:24.220 --> 00:29:27.486
Vieques is likely to be one of
the most contaminated sites in

00:29:27.486 --> 00:29:28.140
the world.
 

00:29:28.140 --> 00:29:30.797
Video voiceover:
 Dr. John Wargo is a Yale

00:29:30.797 --> 00:29:33.787
professor who studies the
effects of toxic exposures on

00:29:33.787 --> 00:29:34.838
human health.
 

00:29:34.838 --> 00:29:37.730
He believes people on the
island are sick because of the

00:29:37.730 --> 00:29:38.940
