00:29:38.940 --> 00:29:40.291
John Wargo,
on video:  This

00:29:40.291 --> 00:29:42.710
contamination results from the
longevity of the bombing,

00:29:42.710 --> 00:29:44.529
the shelling,
the strafing,

00:29:44.529 --> 00:29:47.750
and many different compounds
were released,

00:29:47.750 --> 00:29:49.640
including lead and mercury and
