00:29:49.640 --> 00:29:52.470
as well as flame retardants,
fuels,

00:29:52.470 --> 00:31:01.140
and many of these were released
in great intensity.

00:31:01.140 --> 00:31:08.866
Video voiceover:
: So, do you think this island

00:31:08.866 --> 00:31:11.200
